{"tid":46040,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"(26學神)有無巴打練車個整試過比死氣喉辣親","createTime":"2016-12-19T11:30:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-07T15:20:15.000Z","uid":12416,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"47590edb41ef4ea307fcbc88ca33ac6502222641","tid":46040,"uid":12416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T11:30:19.000Z","msg":"琴晚練車唔小心比死氣喉辣親，睇左醫生開左三日假同打左破傷風針，無奈大後日就考牌兼學牌到期，你地會頂硬上定改期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無巴打試過比死氣喉辣親 跟住點同搞左幾耐好番<br />\n<br />\n慎入<br />\n<a href=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/19/192423_901db0ddb07941064aa3a0fb9b265da2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F19%2F192423_901db0ddb07941064aa3a0fb9b265da2.jpg&d=O2crjNZjBTXnl2NAVqaFXEsIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=e8e80d5a\" target=\"_blank\">https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/19/192423_901db0ddb07941064aa3a0fb9b265da2.jpg</a>"},{"pid":"379c821e309c712e8cb29fead7f900620c08e5b1","tid":46040,"uid":22327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T11:42:42.000Z","msg":"派車後俾條喉壓住 之後每日火酒洗完傷口再灑消炎藥 兩個禮拜好返"},{"pid":"54c0ac72367a8950a95a14b8a415d274d001f014","tid":46040,"uid":33826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T11:50:57.000Z","msg":"你冇著長褲嫁咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4993c92bd3fa5ea5bc3c57bc5e26678b2b8f43b5","tid":46040,"uid":12416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T11:52:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你冇著長褲嫁咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n人生得高 一坐低就chik起條褲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0513b5e35b35d7feca54fbbdcc6f158df8e2b4f7","tid":46040,"uid":1787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T11:53:16.000Z","msg":"2級燒傷，過左一日行街先頂唔住去醫院，醫生話再遲啲要切隻腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da216996a08689a00d91a41dac34ffbeb623ca04","tid":46040,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T11:53:38.000Z","msg":"細個試過<br />\n到依家都有啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9d840202efe971c2605b3fdf120c08242538ca4","tid":46040,"uid":29584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T12:02:05.000Z","msg":"我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係係辣親隻手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90cce32322a0c59544a345bebcc2907306514ae8","tid":46040,"uid":56310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T12:13:22.000Z","msg":"細個去泰國試過，當地醫生話啲壞死皮膚會有細菌感染，佢就咁用啲消毒藥水搽下叫我返屋企日日浸腳,然後刮走啲皮同肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。成個月先好返，不過有疤痕"},{"pid":"1c83ae26c4d573d35c8e91f2156e8327e4e5f589","tid":46040,"uid":61087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T12:13:57.000Z","msg":"學院車？有護架應該唔會壓住"},{"pid":"6fd2f75aa67123822c0fb22106e1053ad41ff520","tid":46040,"uid":36791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T12:15:12.000Z","msg":"未試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f692588848ada87c9664fc59c0c3729ad6f9969","tid":46040,"uid":51387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T02:13:10.000Z","msg":"我就唔敢睇. 不過奉勸巴打唔好去考, 留屋企抖下唔好因咩事令傷口惡化. <br />\n最多咪好返之後再做過學牌考過, 連補鐘頂到盡幾千. <br />\n<br />\n幾千蚊買唔返隻腳. <br />\n嚴重燒傷處理得唔好, 細菌感染隨時截肢"},{"pid":"909ff93d8a561bc89a730aeffffddae20c96f43e","tid":46040,"uid":46669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T05:36:53.000Z","msg":"我前幾個禮拜學著長褲長襪都熱到唔敢掂到死氣喉<br />\n揸棍真係唔好貪型著吊腳褲摺褲腳<br />\n真係想型建議你考慮下買番條電單車褲著係面保護下對腳"},{"p