lyTime":"2016-12-21T03:35:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好講死氣喉 引擎外殻都熱撚到痴線 其實我反而好奇點解揸左咁耐都唔會俾佢辣到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係喎...未試過辣到<br />\n條褲夠長,有時FEEL到啲熱氣喺褲管出面"},{"pid":"63331272a8ba7b71f2cdef204b64c61f525cc67e","tid":46040,"uid":10094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T03:41:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔好講死氣喉 引擎外殻都熱撚到痴線 其實我反而好奇點解揸左咁耐都唔會俾佢辣到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係喎...未試過辣到<br />\n條褲夠長,有時FEEL到啲熱氣喺褲管出面</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有時腳眼會feel到熱 但係點都唔會辣親 真係世界一大迷團<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81fea15ee6b3fbc634042aba410409868d3f580d","tid":46040,"uid":8598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T05:23:52.000Z","msg":"好恐怖，樓主俾條死氣喉壓住？"},{"pid":"83a0b3efcac69e1f3b4f8a287ae7f673f740f2f5","tid":46040,"uid":4179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T10:23:51.000Z","msg":"Take care<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都學緊 依家好驚添"},{"pid":"92afc9630a48cf5022bc6f3cd648d8e3b433f82d","tid":46040,"uid":64415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T11:21:24.000Z","msg":"考，少少傷怕咩"},{"pid":"31a019e51fa59da57c6b63fe1c89e1111e320baf","tid":46040,"uid":16812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T11:55:12.000Z","msg":"練起頭失平衡，隻右腳hi咗落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n鐵板燒咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一開始無乜感覺，之後自己剪走咗啲皮，再用鹽水洗傷口同貼敷料貼咗兩個禮拜到好返咗7成左右，圖就唔貼了，費事比人起底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a81cbcb15ea816afecaf672ed3034918458ede3","tid":46040,"uid":56511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T23:06:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>派車後俾條喉壓住 之後每日火酒洗完傷口再灑消炎藥 兩個禮拜好返</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n聽到都覺得痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6960c3c3e2476c934719212d9318634de80e6f2","tid":46040,"uid":56511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T23:23:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇左咁耐先睇到係26屌 諗左好撚耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}